.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-CAPACITY-VARIANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-capacity-variance \- FEAT-2420 variance of channel capacities
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-capacity-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the statistical variance of channel capacities (local_msat + remote_msat) across all channels (FEAT-2420).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
